data.agents
Class AgentStorage

java.lang.Object
  data.agents.AgentStorage
Direct Known Subclasses:
AgentStorageMySQL
public abstract class AgentStorage
extends java.lang.Object

AgentStorage provides a number of defined methods to mutate and retrieve Agent properties. There can only be one AgentStorage per application, which is set via the setInstance(AgentStorage) method.

Author:
W.H. Mook
